skins.selfIntroduction: From my sister Z23 forth, we were all assigned code names. However, no matter what I am called or where I am deployed, I shall fulfill my duties!
skins.acquisition: 1936-A class destroyer Z25, reporting in. Please be at ease, I shall do my utmost in battle.
skins.login: You're right on time. Well then, I should also get fired up.
skins.details: Mr. Anchor, what must I do to become as outstanding as my sister...?
skins.secretaryIdle1: Z23... is probably engrossed in her studies right now...
skins.secretaryIdle2: Research plans... commission schedule... Ugh... this is no time to be getting sleepy...
skins.secretaryIdle3: This thing here? He- it's really just an ordinary toy!
skins.secretaryTouch: Zzz.... woah! Sorry, I shouldn't have been daydreaming...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Oooh! ...If that was on purpose, you'd better grit your teeth!

skins.shipDescription: Even at the beach, we cannot afford to be careless! Commander, have you adequately prepared for today's activities?
skins.acquisition: Even at the beach, we cannot afford to be careless! Commander, have you adequately prepared for today's activities?
skins.login: Phew... It's been a long time since I've been able to enjoy such a refreshing breeze.
skins.details: Mr. Anchor has to sit out in the sun as well, or he will get moldy.
skins.secretaryIdle1: Volleyball? Or how about swimming! I won't lose, no matter what you pick!
skins.secretaryIdle2: Liven up! Don't tell me you're tired already!
skins.secretaryIdle3: It's time to let these Royals witness the tactics and teamwork of the Iron Blood! Heheh~
skins.secretaryTouch: I'm not tired yet, there's no need for you to massage- Ooh... that feels pretty good...
